Package: ylistjp
Title: Unofficial Access to YList Japanese Plant Name Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        given = "ylistjp",
        family = "contributors",
        email = "noreply@example.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Author: ylistjp contributors
Maintainer: ylistjp contributors <noreply@example.com>
Description: Fetches and caches the public tab-delimited YList data file and
    provides helpers for looking up scientific plant names from Japanese names.
    It also includes a small optional helper for checking scientific names
    against the GBIF species match API. This package is not affiliated with or
    endorsed by YList.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/maple60/ylistjp, https://maple60.github.io/ylistjp/
